  "title": "1 year Laboratory Assistant  - $2300 #HMS",
  "description": "<p>Office hours, Mon to Fri<br />Location: Biopolis (Walkable from Buona Vista)<br />Salary: $2,300<br />Duration: 1 year contract<br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Completing and reviewing work assignments and adjusting workload and resources periodically with the team.</li><li>Mentoring and cross-training staff with a standardized training program and documentation.</li><li>Implementing required quality management systems to ensure customer work scope, results, and team performance meet approved SOPs and organization's safety and quality requirements.</li><li>Participating in cost, quality, and efficiency improvement initiatives driven by the Team Lead.</li><li>Coordinating and ensuring timely calibration of laboratory equipment.</li><li>Maintaining good laboratory housekeeping with the team.</li><li>Additionally, your laboratory operations responsibilities will involve:</li><li>Perfume compounding and material selection as per formulation.</li><li>Updating compounding information in the Electronic Lab Notebook.</li><li>Ensuring clean tools are used for weighing.</li><li>Preparation for odor evaluations.</li><li>Maintaining End-to-End (E2E) service of material management.</li><li>Supporting the shipping of compounded materials with complete shipping documents.</li><li>Operating and maintaining the Contexa robot.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p></p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p><p></p>",
